response: You do not have to be wealthy to adopt. You don't have to own your own home or meet a predetermined income level to be eligible. Your income may come from employment, a pension or disability payments. Both members of a couple may work. Some families, focused on making adoption a reality, have asked family and friends to donate to their adoption fund in lieu of the usual gifts marking celebrations. Want to hear more?
